These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, van, quad-bike, ship
House: craftsman, art-deco, colonial, gothic-revival
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, orange, blood-red, blue
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, monopoly, whist
 1. the craftsman house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4
 3. the person who likes brown is on the left of the colonial house##1
 4. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 5. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 7. the person who likes orange is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing whist and the gothic-revival house##2
10. the person driving the snowmobile is the person playing whist##1
11. the colonial house is the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Transport          | quad-bike  | snowmobile    | ship    | van   |
| House   | art-deco     | craftsman   | colonial       | gothic-revival    |
| Color   | orange | brown | blue    | blood-red |
| Game           | go | whist       | mah-jongg | monopoly     |

