.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, mystery, romance, zombie
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, 7up, fanta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, r&b, d&b, pop
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, electrician, paramedic, police-officer
 1. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
 2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the electrician##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is the fan of indie##1
 5. the police-officer is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 7. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 8. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the doctor##3
 9. the fan of d&b is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching romance movies is in an odd position##4
11. the fan of d&b is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre          | animation  | mystery    | romance     | zombie       |
| Beverage         | 7up | fanta | almond-milk   | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | indie   | r&b   | pop    |
| Job         | paramedic | police-officer  | doctor | electrician   |

