.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, february, november, may
House: palace, gothic-revival, farmhouse, futuristic
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, aristoff, davidoff, game
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, snowboarding, skiing, skateboarding
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 2. the aristoff-smoker is the farmhouse house##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
 4. the palace house is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is the futuristic house##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is the game-smoker##1
 8. the futuristic house is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
10. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's birthday is in november##1
11. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday      | march | november   | may    | february      |
| House           | farmhouse | palace | gothic-revival | futuristic     |
| Cigar   | aristoff      | game   | baccarat   | davidoff |
| Sport           | skateboarding         | soccer       | skiing  | snowboarding       |

