The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, manager, dancer, freelancer
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, montecristo, alhambra, dunhill
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the dancer is on the left of the security-guard##1
 3. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
 4. the manager is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is the dunhill-smoker##1
 6. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
 8. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 9. the alhambra-smoker is the manager##1
10. the havana-smoker is on the left of the security-guard##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is the fan of techno##1
12. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | july       | september   | may   | august   |
| Music-Genre       | funk        | techno | gospel    | electronic       |
| Job      | freelancer | manager    | dancer  | security-guard |
