.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, bridge, whist, domino
City: edinburgh, miami, san-francisco, marseilles
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, baccarat, old-henry, fonseca
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, zinnia, sunflower
 1. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person who growspoppy and the person playing domino##2
 3. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 4. the baccarat-smoker is the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an even position##4
 7. the person playing bridge is the chaman-smoker##1
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is the baccarat-smoker##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
10. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
12. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Game    | whist    | domino      | backgammon          | bridge    |
| City   | miami | marseilles       | san-francisco | edinburgh |
| Cigar     | fonseca     | old-henry      | baccarat     | chaman |
| Flower   | daisy   | sunflower | zinnia        | poppy   |

