.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, june, january, february
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, 7up, tea
4 different games are played: bridge, billiard, go, mah-jongg
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, lily, dahlia, daisy
 1. the person who growsdaisy is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who growsaconite is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who growsdahlia##2
 3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing go##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
 7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person who growsaconite is between the person playing bridge and the person drinking water##2
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
12. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Birthday         | june  | january    | april    | february |
| Beverage   | 7up   | sprite       | water  | tea    |
| Game   | bridge | billiard | go | mah-jongg   |
| Flower           | dahlia    | aconite        | daisy   | lily    |

