City: venice, nizza, london, hamburg
 1. the indian is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 2. the person traveling to london is in an even position##4
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is between the person driving the roller and the person traveling to nizza##2
 4. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
 6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the brazilian##1
 7. the davidoff-smoker is in an odd position##4
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is the person driving the roller##1
 9. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the train##1
11. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
12. the cain-smoker is on the left of the brazilian##1
13. the blend-smoker is on the right of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
