There 4 different types of food: cucumber, grapefruit, papaya, pomegranate
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, van, tram
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person driving the tram and the musician##2
 3. the person eating cucumber is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the architect is between the person eating pomegranate and the musician##2
 5. the person eating papaya is between the lawyer and the musician##2
 6. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
 7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
 9. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
10. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday      | june   | may   | august     | january   |
| Job   | lawyer  | architect       | musician | police-officer |
| Food           | pomegranate     | papaya   | grapefruit     | cucumber     |
| Transport         | tram | van | bus   | quad-bike |

