.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, august, june, february
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, metal, dubstep, pop
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, zinnia, aconite, bellflower
City: prague, new-york, hamburg, san-francisco
 1. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the person who growszinnia is in an even position##4
 5. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 7. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
10. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
11. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
12. the fan of classical is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Birthday      | june       | august | july        | february        |
| Music-Genre         | pop | dubstep       | classical | metal |
| Flower   | bellflower     | zinnia        | daffodil    | aconite      |
| City         | new-york     | hamburg    | san-francisco | prague   |

