.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, mouse, horse, guinea-pig
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, march, february, april
4 different games are played: bridge, backgammon, billiard, chess
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, 7up, tea, soy-milk
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person playing billiard##1
 2. the person playing billiard is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 3. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 5. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
10. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
12. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet   | mouse      | goldfish | guinea-pig     | horse        |
| Birthday   | february | april  | march     | may |
| Game         | backgammon    | bridge | billiard      | chess |
| Beverage     | soy-milk | 7up     | tea | iced-tea       |

 